OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781707674
OL,3,CKatie Price's husband Lee Andrews
OL,4,Creappears claiming he was held at gun
OL,5,Cpoint
OL,7,FKatie Price's husband Lee Andrews has
OL,8,Freappeared on social media weeks after
OL,9,Fgoing "missing", claiming he was held
OL,10,Fat gunpoint on the UAE-Omani border
OL,11,Fand had been detained for "espionage".
OL,13,FThe former glamour model and reality
OL,14,FTV star started a public campaign to
OL,15,Ffind her husband after the 43-year-old
OL,16,FDubai-based businessman failed to show
OL,17,Fup for their joint appearance on ITV's
OL,18,FGood Morning Britain on Tuesday, May
OL,19,F12, claiming he had "things to do".
OL,26,@{D@UOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
