OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781707674
OL,3,CKatie Price's husband Lee Andrews
OL,4,Creappears claiming he was held at gun
OL,5,Cpoint
OL,7,FPrice later claimed producers of the
OL,8,FITV programme had spoken to the
OL,9,FForeign Office, who said they had
OL,10,Fdetained a British man with Lee's name
OL,11,Fand date of birth.
OL,13,FShe did not say which country Andrews,
OL,14,Fwho lives in Dubai, was detained in.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
