OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781707674
OL,3,CKatie Price's husband Lee Andrews
OL,4,Creappears claiming he was held at gun
OL,5,Cpoint
OL,7,FAfter weeks of speculation, Andrews
OL,8,Freappeared on social media with a
OL,9,FFacebook post in the early hours of
OL,10,FWednesday, claiming to have been
OL,11,Fcaptured by men with assault rifles,
OL,12,F"shackled," and a hood put over his
OL,13,Fhead and taken to a black site on
OL,14,Fcharges of espionage.
OL,16,FHe had no use of his phone, he said.
OL,18,FAndrews said the men who captured him
OL,19,Fwere from "an extended arm of the
OL,20,Fnational guard".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
