OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781707674
OL,3,CKatie Price's husband Lee Andrews
OL,4,Creappears claiming he was held at gun
OL,5,Cpoint
OL,7,FAfter his release, he claimed to have
OL,8,Fsigned disclaimers "with state
OL,9,Fsecurity" but did not say which state.
OL,11,F"I can tell you I'm now safe and
OL,12,Fhealthy and with my wife."
OL,14,F"At no point have I faced anything to
OL,15,Fdo with fraud allegations or any
OL,16,Fcriminal activities such as that," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
