OL,3,CKatie Price's husband Lee Andrews
OL,4,Creappears claiming he was held at gun
OL,5,Cpoint
OL,7,FIn a second video, posted Wednesday
OL,8,Fmorning he said: "I am sending these
OL,9,Fmessages out to my loved-ones and my
OL,10,Fbeautiful wife who without her help
OL,11,Finvolving all the UK authorities, I
OL,12,Fdon't think I would have got out of
OL,13,Fthat situation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
