OL,3,CKatie Price's husband Lee Andrews
OL,4,Creappears claiming he was held at gun
OL,5,Cpoint
OL,7,F"Because of the tensions and things
OL,8,Fhappening in the region and me being
OL,9,Fso close to the border, this is why I
OL,10,Fwas suspected of espionage and held in
OL,11,Fa state security building without the
OL,12,Fuse of a telephone and any rights,
OL,13,Fsuch as a shower, contact or speak to
OL,14,Fanybody, including the embassy or my
OL,15,Fwife.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
