OL,3,CKatie Price's husband Lee Andrews
OL,4,Creappears claiming he was held at gun
OL,5,Cpoint
OL,7,F"So thank you to Katie for making such
OL,8,Fa noise that the UAE actually listened
OL,9,Fand let me go. From there I did have a
OL,10,Fcivil case in Dubai, which led to me
OL,11,Fgoing into the mainstream prison
OL,12,Fduring the Arabic holiday Eid and I
OL,13,Fwas able to secure my release."
OL,15,FPrice has flown out to Dubai to be
OL,16,Fwith her husband. The former glamour
OL,17,Fmodel and reality TV star had
OL,18,Fpreviously claimed Andrews had been
OL,19,Finterrogated on suspicion of being "a
OL,20,Fspy".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
