OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FPrice and Andrews were married in
OL,13,FJanuary, just days after they met in
OL,14,Fperson in Dubai.
OL,16,FIt is Price's fourth marriage. She
OL,17,Ffirst wed Australian singer Peter
OL,18,FAndre in 2005, eventually getting
OL,19,Fdivorced in 2009. She was married to
OL,20,Fcage fighter Alex Reid between 2010
OL,21,Fand 2012.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
